00:07:52.538 --> 00:07:54.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>No self-respecting Englishman would.</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:54.577 --> 00:07:57.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pabst! Pabst, get out here.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:57.776 --> 00:08:00.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's wrong now, Herb?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-One guess.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:00.655 --> 00:08:02.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Battle of the doughnuts," round 28.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:02.415 --> 00:08:05.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? You call me out here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to complain? About the doughnuts?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:05.614 --> 00:08:06.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're stale again.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:09.532 --> 00:08:10.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Delicious.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:10.492 --> 00:08:12.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Delicious, my eye.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>These are two days old, and you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:12.852 --> 00:08:14.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been eating doughnuts my whole life.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:14.611 --> 00:08:17.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>These weren't baked more than...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Six hours ago.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:17.610 --> 00:08:19.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it. I quit.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going over to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>galaxy.</i></c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:20.101 --> 00:08:21.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Galaxy?</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> That rag?</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:21.329 --> 00:08:22.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>HERB: That rag knows the difference</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between doughnuts and doorstops.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:22.648 --> 00:08:23.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Whose winning?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Draw, same as always.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:24.484 --> 00:08:27.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Want to write in </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>galaxy?</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They won't pay four cents a word.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:27.727 --> 00:08:29.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're paying him four cents a word?</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:29.486 --> 00:08:31.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Stay out, Julius.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-ALBERT: Where did I put?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:31.125 --> 00:08:32.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I gave you the matches.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I gave them to you.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:32.886 --> 00:08:36.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>For that fantasy crap you write,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're lucky to get two.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:36.165 --> 00:08:37.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-ALBERT: Maybe I put them over there.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-JULIUS: I beg your pardon?</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:37.164 --> 00:08:38.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The latest </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>galaxy.</i></c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:39.803 --> 00:08:41.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>KAY: Benny has the new issue of </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Galaxy.</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:41.603 --> 00:08:42.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me see that.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:47.281 --> 00:08:50.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Heinlein, Bradbury, Sturgeon.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:51.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite a lineup.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:53.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Add Herbert Rossoff to them,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it'd be complete.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:54.438 --> 00:08:56.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if I promise you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>fresh doughnuts tomorrow?</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:56.879 --> 00:08:59.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Why should I believe you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll even throw in a couple of crullers.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:59.758 --> 00:09:02.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Okay, I'll stay.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't do us any favors.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:02.716 --> 00:09:07.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good. Now that we've finished</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>With the old business, on to the new.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:07.195 --> 00:09:09.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Time to hand out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>next month's story assignments.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:09.594 --> 00:09:10.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ritterhouse, we're waiting!</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:10.954 --> 00:09:12.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay, friends and neighbors.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:13.340 --> 00:09:15.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's see what uncle Roy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has for you today.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:15.312 --> 00:09:18.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>PABST: All right, I've titled this one</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"Please take me with you."</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:18.112 --> 00:09:21.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Who wants it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Kay: what do you think, Jules?</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:22.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>JULIUS: I think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can do something with that.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:22.631 --> 00:09:25.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'll bet you can. I can see it now...</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:25.350 --> 00:09:27.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lonely little girl befriended</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by empathetic aliens</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:27.949 --> 00:09:29.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who teach her how to smile.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:30.108 --> 00:09:32.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's enough to make you go out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and buy a television set.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:32.228 --> 00:09:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:33.227 --> 00:09:35.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROY: This is Mr. Pabst's favorite,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"honeymoon on Andorras."</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:36.386 --> 00:09:37.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got to be kidding.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:37.626 --> 00:09:39.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had too much sauerkraut</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my franks that night.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:39.905 --> 00:09:41.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What can I say?</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:41.545 --> 00:09:43.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is the worst garbage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have ever seen.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:44.144 --> 00:09:45.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you. I'll take it.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:45.743 --> 00:09:48.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, you will. You have an affinity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for garbage. Don't you?</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:48.423 --> 00:09:52.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The picture may be garbage,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but the story... The story will be art.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:52.621 --> 00:09:53.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Others scoffing )</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:57.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>PABST: All right, I haven't got a title</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for this one yet.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:57.380 --> 00:10:00.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Anybody got any ideas?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll think of something.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:04.138 --> 00:10:07.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>PABST: All right, next order of business.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some of our readers have been writing in</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:07.537 --> 00:10:09.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>wanting to know what you people look like.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:09.216 --> 00:10:10.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KAY: well, write back and tell them</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:10.216 --> 00:10:13.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We look like writers, poor, needy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and incredibly attractive.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:13.815 --> 00:10:15.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, our publisher has a better idea.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:15.375 --> 00:10:17.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Stone has decided to run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a picture of you</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:17.414 --> 00:10:18.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in next month's issue.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:19.333 --> 00:10:20.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that absolutely...</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:20.493 --> 00:10:22.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Necessary? I'm afraid it is.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:23.527 --> 00:10:24.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kay, you can sleep late that day.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:25.692 --> 00:10:26.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, I can.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:27.331 --> 00:10:30.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>God forbid the public ever finds out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That K.C. Hunter is a woman.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:30.730 --> 00:10:32.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose I'm sleeping late that day, too.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:33.569 --> 00:10:35.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not personal, but as far</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as our readers are concerned,</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:35.808 --> 00:10:38.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny Russell is as white as they are.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Let's keep it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:39.476 --> 00:10:39.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Sarcastically ) Oh, yes...</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:40.735 --> 00:10:42.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the world's not ready</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a woman writer...</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:42.206 --> 00:10:45.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Imagine what would happen if it learned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about a Negro with a typewriter.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:46.645 --> 00:10:49.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run for the hills.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's the end of civilization.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:49.685 --> 00:10:52.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about W.E.B. Dubois,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Zora Neale Huston,</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:52.683 --> 00:10:56.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Langston Hughes, Ralph Ellison,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Richard Wright?</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:56.682 --> 00:10:57.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you ever hear of</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> native son?</i></c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:57.961 --> 00:11:00.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's literature for liberals</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and intellectuals.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:00.721 --> 00:11:03.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The average reader won't spend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his hard-earned cash</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On stories written by Negroes.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:06.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someone shoot me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and put me out of my misery.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:06.479 --> 00:11:10.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, how I long for a gun.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Sorry, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:10.718 --> 00:11:11.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish things were different,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but they're not.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:12.318 --> 00:11:13.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wishing never changed a damn thing.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:14.117 --> 00:11:15.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on, Benny, it's just a photo.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:16.636 --> 00:11:17.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try to remember that.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:21.915 --> 00:11:22.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a dog.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:27.113 --> 00:11:29.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, enough standing around.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get back to work.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:32.592 --> 00:11:34.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Typewriter clattering )</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:49.586 --> 00:11:50.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hey, hey.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:51.346 --> 00:11:54.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's the hurry?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's my drawing.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:54.425 --> 00:11:56.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is that so?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nice suit.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:56.544 --> 00:11:57.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where'd you get it?</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:59.103 --> 00:11:59.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I bought it.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:00.583 --> 00:12:02.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I have my drawing back?</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:02.422 --> 00:12:06.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, boy, I'd watch that tone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of voice if I were you.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:06.461 --> 00:12:07.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:07.621 --> 00:12:08.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I work here.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:08.740 --> 00:12:09.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>RYAN: Yeah? Where?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:09.740 --> 00:12:10.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In there.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:11.820 --> 00:12:12.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you? The janitor?</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:13.779 --> 00:12:15.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Awfully well-dressed for a janitor.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:16.984 --> 00:12:17.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do we know that picture's yours?</c.bg_transparent>

204
