624
00:36:33.262 --> 00:36:34.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's his decision.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:36.100 --> 00:36:38.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you can't fire me.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:39.203 --> 00:36:42.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I quit. To hell with you...</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:43.658 --> 00:36:45.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And to hell with Stone.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:45.938 --> 00:36:47.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to stay calm, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:47.298 --> 00:36:51.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! I'm tired of being calm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Calm never got me a damn thing.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:36:51.416 --> 00:36:52.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm warning you, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:52.376 --> 00:36:54.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't stop this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to call the police.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:54.856 --> 00:36:56.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You go ahead! Call them!</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:36:57.214 --> 00:37:00.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call anybody you want.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They can't do anything to me.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:00.494 --> 00:37:02.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore... And nor can any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:08.916 --> 00:37:12.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... Am a human being, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:13.809 --> 00:37:19.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can deny me all you want...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But you cannot deny Ben Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:19.248 --> 00:37:20.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He exists.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:37:20.687 --> 00:37:25.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future, that space station,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those people, they exist in here.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:26.806 --> 00:37:32.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In my mind. I created it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And every one of you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:32.524 --> 00:37:33.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You read it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:34.324 --> 00:37:37.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's here. You get what I'm telling you?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:38.431 --> 00:37:42.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can pulp a story,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:42.441 --> 00:37:44.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That's ancient knowledge.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:37:44.960 --> 00:37:47.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:37:49.639 --> 00:37:53.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:37:54.117 --> 00:37:56.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:37:56.677 --> 00:38:01.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real! I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:02.196 --> 00:38:05.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's real. Oh, god!</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:06.554 --> 00:38:08.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Weeping )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:19.590 --> 00:38:20.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PARAMEDIC: Easy...</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:33.706 --> 00:38:34.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One... two... three.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:55.499 --> 00:38:57.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest easy, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:57.498 --> 00:39:00.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have walked in the path</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:39:00.458 --> 00:39:02.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no greater glory.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:39:03.174 --> 00:39:04.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, please.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:39:05.296 --> 00:39:06.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:39:07.163 --> 00:39:08.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you know?</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:39:08.775 --> 00:39:09.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:39:10.934 --> 00:39:13.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the dreamer...</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:39:14.213 --> 00:39:16.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:39:31.449 --> 00:39:32.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KASIDY: Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:34.328 --> 00:39:35.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ben?</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:45.244 --> 00:39:47.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How long was I out?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Only for a few minutes.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:39:48.523 --> 00:39:50.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seemed like forever to me.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:39:51.402 --> 00:39:52.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's odd.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:39:53.423 --> 00:39:55.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow your neural patterns</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have returned to normal.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:39:55.681 --> 00:39:58.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's good, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, it's very good.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:39:58.321 --> 00:40:00.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't understand how it happened.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:07.837 --> 00:40:09.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling, son?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:10.116 --> 00:40:11.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm okay.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:12.596 --> 00:40:14.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm done packing.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:14.995 --> 00:40:17.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Transport leaves at 8:00 in the morning.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:18.274 --> 00:40:20.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish you could stay longer.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:40:20.993 --> 00:40:22.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get back to the restaurant.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:40:23.712 --> 00:40:26.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My customers have never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gone this long without me.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:40:28.271 --> 00:40:31.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is what are you going to do?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:40:33.830 --> 00:40:38.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only thing I can do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Stay here and finish the job I started,</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:40:39.748 --> 00:40:41.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if I fail...</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:40:41.387 --> 00:40:46.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I have fought the good fight...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have finished the course...</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:40:47.259 --> 00:40:49.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have kept the faith."</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:40:50.505 --> 00:40:52.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never known you to quote</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the bible.</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:52.904 --> 00:40:55.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm full of surprises, aren't I?</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:40:57.263 --> 00:40:58.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:40:59.822 --> 00:41:03.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sounds like that dream</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you had... Helped you sort things out.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:41:04.501 --> 00:41:05.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose it did...</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:41:07.140 --> 00:41:09.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have begun to wonder.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:10.338 --> 00:41:11.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it wasn't a dream?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:13.138 --> 00:41:16.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if this life we're leading,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of this...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:17.977 --> 00:41:24.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and me, everything...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What if all of this is the illusion?</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:25.614 --> 00:41:27.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a scary thought.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:28.493 --> 00:41:29.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I know.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:41:30.573 --> 00:41:32.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe, just maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:41:32.972 --> 00:41:34.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny isn't the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:41:35.115 --> 00:41:35.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:41:36.891 --> 00:41:41.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we're nothing more than figments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his imagination.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:41:43.497 --> 00:41:44.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For all we know...</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:41:45.848 --> 00:41:47.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this very moment,</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:41:47.728 --> 00:41:52.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somewhere far beyond</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those distant stars...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:41:53.406 --> 00:41:54.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny Russell...</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:41:55.605 --> 00:41:57.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is dreaming of us.</c.bg_transparent>

